creator: Vite Biz
descriptionHtml:
Evaluate your IELTS writing and speaking scores in seconds! You can track your own progress with visualized graphs and improve your performance.
For writing tasks analysis IELTS Analyst, supplies you with artificial intelligence powered analysis of written content with Sentiments, Emotions, Entities, Categories, Grammar Mistakes and detailed explanation on it. Graphs of improvements of performance which can trackable and gives you confidence enough.
For speaking tasks our machine learning based video analysis will help you to understand your speaking results with audio to text analysis as well as focused keyword analysis. It uses key phrases used in your test and emotions during giving answers.

title: IELTS Analyst For Writing And Speaking Practice

creator: Vite Biz
descriptionHtml:
Start your journey from beginner to IELTS 7+ bands in less than 4 weeks

Prepare for your IELTS test with a range of free IELTS mock tests and evaluate yourself with the AI-powered platform.

Prepare with confidence for your upcoming IELTS Test. IELTS analyst will help you to achieve your goals with the Academic or General Training test. The IELTS Analyst App gives you instant, unlimited access to all the tests and tools you need to prepare for your test – anytime, anywhere.

Writing Tasks Analysis

IELTS Analyst supplies you with artificial intelligence-powered analysis of written content with
Coherence and Cohesion with Sentiments Analysis
Emotions Analysis
Entities or Topics Covered
Categories or Subjects Covered
Grammatical Range and Accuracy with the highlighted explanation of them.

Graphs of improvements in performance that can be trackable and give you confidence enough.

Speaking Tests Analysis

IELTS Analyst’s machine learning based video analysis will help you to understand your speaking results.

Pronunciation (Audio to Text) analysis
Fluency and coherence analysis
Emotions Analysis
Lexical resource used

Reading Tests Analysis

The IELTS Reading test consists of 40 questions, designed to test a wide range of reading skills. IELTS Analyst helps you to prepare for tests with mock tests which include reading for gist, reading for main ideas, reading for detail, skimming, understanding logical arguments and recognizing writers' opinions, attitudes and purpose.

Listening Tests Analysis

IELTS Analyst will help you to prepare for the listening test in which you need to answer 40 questions based on recordings. You need to answer questions connected to the recordings ranging from multiple choice to matching information, headings, features and sentence endings, as well as sentence, summary, note, table, diagram or flow-chart completion.
